title: Legenda o Tile
actors: Lembit Ulfsak, Natalya Belokhvostikova, Evgeniy Leonov, Mikhail Ulyanov, Larisa Malevannaya, Alla Demidova, Anatoliy Solonitsyn, Innokentiy Smoktunovskiy, Igor Ledogorov, Vera Vasileva, Juozas Budraitis, Mikaela Drozdovskaya, Vladislav Dvorzhetskiy, Evgeniy Evstigneev, Vladimir Fyodorov
description: A story of two orphans growing up in Flemish town at the time of witch-hunts, fear and ever present chance to get caught and been tortured and killed with or without a reason.
